data.description: Introducing this beautiful 2 Story home with a traditional, yet modern floor plan located in award-winning School District 203 and highly sought after Farmington sub-division, offers one of the best educations Naperville has to offer, highlighting Riverwoods Elementary, Madison Jr and Naperville Central. Enter through the stunning Portico inviting you into the charming sitting room at the entrance. The interior boasts hardwood flooring throughout.  The large, updated Kitchen is a true gem, featuring stainless steel appliances, large center island, granite countertops and ample cooking space for preparing meals and creating memories.  The adjoining spacious family room provides the perfect setting for relaxation around the gas start fireplace.  With 4 Bedrooms and 2.5 Baths, there's abundant space for everyone. Additionally, the basement offers a potential 5th Bedroom, roughed in plumbing for bath and fantastic soundproof theater room.    In addition, the attached 2 car garage has a brand-new door in 2020 and for added security a fully equipped hardwired camera system, 24-hour loop, with 30 day DVR.   There are so many new updates: sump pump 2023, new driveway and concrete front entrance in 2022, newer wrought iron fence, New Hot water tank 2021, washer & dryer 2023, dishwasher 2022, newer furnace, new whole house April Air 2023, new Great Escape pool 2021, the hall bathroom upstairs was upgraded in 2023, all new toilets throughout.  The roof is 50 years with 37 remaining. Finally: Imagine having the fantastic Farmington Park right in your backyard! You'll have endless opportunities for outdoor activities and enjoying nature
